text: The United International Mansion () is a late-modernist skyscraper made of reinforced concrete in Chongqing, China completed in 2013. As of 2014, it has the 8th-highest Helipad in the world at 286m (942 ft).https://global.ctbuh.org/resources/papers/1812-Journal2014_IssueII_TBIN.pdf ==See also== *List of tallest buildings in Chongqing *List of tallest buildings in China ==References== Category:2013 establishments in China Category:Office buildings completed in 2013 Category:Skyscraper office buildings in Chongqing Category:Buildings and structures in Chongqing Category:Skyscrapers in Chongqing
